AC coupled System,Chapter Three: Safety in PV system,PV system Installation safety, International Fire and Safety Standards, Ladder specification, Personal Fall Arrest System, Safety Nets, Guard Rail Lockout-Tag out, Chapter Four:  Electricity fundamental, Voltage, Current, Power, Energy, battery power, Series, parallel connection, and basic Electrical formula,Chapter Five: Fundamentals Solar Energy, Solar Power, Solar Energy, Tilt Angles, Rule of Thumb, Shading, Type of Solar radiation, Chapter Six: Fundamental of Solar Pv Modules,Working Principle of Solar PV, Difference Between Cell, Module and Array, Poly, Mono Cell, Types of Diode used in PV module, Open Circuit Voltage, Short Circuit voltage, PV module Label, IV curve, Chapter Seven: Solar PV System Component,Solar PV Module with respect to No. of Cells, Interactive Inverter, Hybrid Inverter, AC Module, Power Optimiser, MC4 Connectors, Wire, OPCD, Fuse Disconnect, MPPT charge Controller, Chapter Eight: Design of PV System, Complete Grid Tied System Design including DC Wire Size, AC Wire Size, and AC over current protection protective device OCPD, DC over current protection protective device DC OCPD, Fuse calculation, Maximum-Minimum no. of series PV module, No. Of Parallel Strings, No of String per MPPT, Maximum String on the inverter, Cable Losses Calculation, Chapter Nine: Mechanical Design of Solar System, Type of mounting system, Ground Mounting, Penetration System, Pole Mounting System, Single Axis Tracker, Dual Axis Tracker Sealants, Fastener, Chapter Ten, Commissioning of Solar Performance Analysis, Maintenance, and troubleshooting, System Visual Inspection, Test the System, Verification of System operation, IR Test, Troubleshooting of PV system, Commissioning checklist and site survey checklist
